      "text": "The hands of a clock cover $360^\\circ$\nin one rotation. How many degrees\nwill the minute hand turn\nbetween 10'clock and 50'clock?\nThe minute hand covers $360^\\circ$ in 60-\nmin (1 hour)\nBetween 10'clock and 5'o clock\nthere are 4 hours.\nThe minutes hand will make\n$= 4 \\times 360^\\circ = 1440^\\circ$\ncoverings\nThe minute hand will turn 1440\ndegrees between 1'o clock and\n5'o clock."
